<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Foro de Pixel Art</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            background-color: #1e1e2e;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #6b6bff);
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .header-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .search-bar {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d3d3d3, #a9a9a9);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .search-bar input {
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            padding: 5px;
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            background: transparent;
        }
        .search-bar img {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
        }
        .button {
            background: #ffcc00;
            color: #1e1e2e;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: 2px solid #ff6b6b;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: #fff;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #2e2e3e;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .post {
            background: #3e3e5e;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }
        .post:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }
        .post h3 {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }
        .post img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 4px solid #ff6b6b;
        }
        .post p {
            color: #fff;
        }
        .comment-section {
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .comment {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1e1e2e;
            background: #ffcc00;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
        }
        .forum-encargos {
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Foro de Pixel Art</h1>
        <div class="header-right">
            <button class="button">Crear Foro</button>
            <div class="search-bar">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Buscar...">
                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/622/622669.png" alt="Lupa">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="post">
            <h3>Usuario1</h3>
            <p>Este es mi nuevo post en el foro. ¡Miren esta foto!</p>
            <img src="https://www.pixelstalk.net/wp-content/uploads/images6/Pixel-Art-Wallpaper-HD.png" alt="Imagen subida">
            <div class="comment-section">
                <div class="comment">Usuario2: ¡Genial foto!</div>
                <div class="comment">Usuario3: Me encanta la vista.</div>
            </div>
            <button class="button forum-encargos">Foro Encargos</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="post">
            <h3>Usuario4</h3>
            <p>Hola a todos, comparto una nueva imagen.</p>
            <img src="https://www.pixelstalk.net/wp-content/uploads/images1/Best-Pixel-Art-Backgrounds-HD.png" alt="Imagen subida">
            <div class="comment-section">
                <div class="comment">Usuario5: ¡Muy bonito!</div>
            </div>
            <button class="button forum-encargos">Foro Encargos</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
